Package: misuvi
Type: Package
Title: Access the 'Michigan Substance Use Vulnerablility Index'
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Brenden Smith
Maintainer: Brenden Smith <brendensmithmi@gmail.com>
Description: Use this package to easily access the MI-SUVI data sets.
    Easily import data sets with full metrics, percentiles,
    Z-scores, or rankings. This package also includes a function to import 
    shape files for easy mapping and a function to access the full technical
    documentation. All data is sourced from Michigan.gov/OpioidsData.
License: CC0
URL: https://github.com/brendensm/misuvi
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
Imports:
  sf,
  tigris
